{"tid":2233362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「求減薪」港龍工會晤資方冀減薪代裁員 國泰拒絕承諾","createTime":"2020-10-07T05:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T01:04:00.000Z","uid":73915,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"865eb8b3c9d431ef364a603d9bafd20a549f4b3b","tid":2233362,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=7fef8448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名榜跌出三甲的國泰航空，以及旗下國泰港龍航空，早前獲政府注資近300億港元，以及批出第1期保就業計劃約7億港元工資補貼後，宣布不參加第2期保就業，被質疑為大裁員鋪路，外界盛傳最快月內向逾千名員工派「大信封」。港龍空勤人員協會今(6日)與國泰管理層會面，希望齊上齊落，建議削減薪酬福利代替裁員，惟國泰仍拒承諾不裁員。"},{"pid":"34d7b3983ee4e14224d6db3670a858e897abc4fa","tid":2233362,"uid":16061,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"咪落返地下做樓面囉 唔洗死嘅"},{"pid":"a817570326eaa34a2305a192728303b56e08c185","tid":2233362,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34d7b3983ee4e14224d6db3670a858e897abc4fa","tid":2233362,"uid":16061,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"咪落返地下做樓面囉 唔洗死嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2498ba08f7e86a0b0c9940fd10a63d32f8ad466e","tid":2233362,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"$0人工，再倒貼<br />\n我估都有好多空姐扑住去做"},{"pid":"0a7ff074e7e1b08b382af3549edbe5f33fbd72a9","tid":2233362,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死"},{"pid":"53d99609e583dba6e9fdfa9da